		"™ (16550—16700) — 10-11 frames (confirmed by hero of the day).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[del 
			"Fix the embarrassing mistake in the dropdown section (16800), shoot some doors on the way if possible — 0-1 frames
		]del
		" (confirmed, not a mistake).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[del 
			"See if boosting off of another corner at the bottom of the OTES can save a frame
		]del
		" (confirmed, possible to do but the frame has to be sacrificed regardless).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Implement second CWJ in the OMBR (17800—17900) — 2 frames (confirmed).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[del 
			"Gain back a phantom frame on the elevator
		]del
		" (confirmed, I actually 
